en: An array of exciting car for rent deals are waiting just for you! We have a complete range of vehicles to accommodate all your needs, whether for corporate purpose or personal pleasure
id: Sejumlah mobil menarik untuk disewa sedang menunggu untuk Anda! Kami memiliki rangkaian lengkap kendaraan untuk mengakomodasi semua kebutuhan Anda, baik untuk tujuan perusahaan atau kesenangan pribadi

en: We offer RELIABLE services guided by our core values of Responsible, Excellent, Lean, Integrity, Adaptive, Better, Loyal and Empower
We offer world-class service with track record of the highest safety standard
MPM Rent is focused on maintaining a safe working environment throughout the company to ensure customer satisfaction & employee well-being
In carrying out it roles, duties, and responsibilities, the Company applies values and corporate cultures contained in the following three CREDO elements
We believe in the power of ideas. No matter where they come from, we embrace new ideas and new knowledge to help us progress
We believe our actions will impact others
Being excited to take personal ownership of our actions and being proactive will lead to the success of our ecosystem
We believe that the most impactful realization of our dreams happens when we work jointly together and remove our constraints to deliver the collective power of our people
We want to be part of your business
id: Kami ingin menjadi bagian dari bisnis Anda

en: To request a quote or want to meet up some coffee, contact us directly or fill out the form, and we will get back to you promptly
id: Untuk meminta penawaran atau ingin bertemu, hubungi kami langsung atau isi formulir, dan kami akan segera menghubungi Anda

en: As we are customer centric transportation services company, we ensure you the utmost reliability in our well-maintained fleet and the whole experience of renting car is smooth, fast, and hassle-free.
id: Karena kami adalah perusahaan layanan transportasi yang berpusat pada pelanggan, kami memastikan Anda mendapatkan keandalan terbaik dalam armada kami yang terawat baik dan seluruh pengalaman menyewa mobil berjalan mulus, cepat, dan tanpa kerumitan.
